Lee Daniels' The Butler;;2013;;PG-13;;Biography,Drama;;7.2;;Lee Daniels;;Forest Whitaker,Oprah Winfrey,John Cusack,Jane Fonda,David Banner,Michael Rainey Jr.,LaJessie Smith,Mariah Carey,Alex Pettyfer,Vanessa Redgrave,Aml Ameen,Clarence Williams III,John P. Fertitta,Jim Gleason,Isaac White,David Oyelowo,Joe Chrest,Colman Domingo;;This film tells the story of Cecil Gaines (Forest Whitaker), a White House butler who served eight American presidents over three decades. The film traces the dramatic changes that swept American society during this time, from the civil rights movement to Vietnam and beyond, and how those changes affected this man's life and family.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1327773/